# The Worker serves data/client-only.json byte-for-byte from raw.githubusercontent.com and
# derives its ETag from a hash of the content. Committing CRLF from a Windows editor would
# change every byte of the file and churn the ETag for no reason, so pin LF.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.js   text eol=lf
*.yml  text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf
